data.title: Dean’s Circle
data.meta_description: More than 75 years of transformational research and hands-on social impact for a better world.
data.text:
As a special way to honor and acknowledge our most generous donors who express their commitment to our school’s mission to improve population health, especially for the most vulnerable, we welcome you to our Dean’s Circle. By contributing $1,000 or more in a fiscal year (July 1 – June 30), you are among our most loyal supporters and we are grateful for your partnership.

Since 2006, Berkeley Public Health’s Dean’s Circle has been a community of committed individual benefactors who share in and support the Dean’s vision for the school’s future by making annual leadership gifts. Your collective generosity inspires others to follow your example.
